{"tid":989864,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好似鍾意咗男朋友daddy...","createTime":"2019-01-21T07:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T01:19:33.000Z","uid":431,"like":31,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"97aab268a451b4e397928dc25102427c8338fa70","tid":989864,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"上個月第一次去男朋友屋企食飯<br />\n一上到去見到佢爸b，我呆咗<br />\n<br />\n未見過一個中佬可以咁正！除咗塊面有少少皺紋之外完全唔似四十幾歲<br />\n真正男人四十一枝花！飽滿胸肌，巧克力塊腹肌，3D倒三角&hellip; <br />\n又溫柔，正過男友多多聲<br />\n<br />\n而重點係我男友係單親家庭，而佢爸b仲未有第二春<br />\n嗰次食飯佢有讚我好成熟，係咪代表我有機會？<br />\n如果我真係想追佢，但佢又大我廿年左右，可以點做？求教！"},{"pid":"a6b9137de47f270795914a8c8db2a200c03cbc86","tid":989864,"uid":115949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"追住黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a609a54b1384906b56e72e4c520c2e1887c6144","tid":989864,"uid":55657,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:35:53.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556ef8b3d4980b1ea33ebeced60c12f46dbf214a","tid":989864,"uid":182499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e4a16c9863101118f80be8fbade462f86aa071","tid":989864,"uid":148056,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">義父生中出</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3d6196b995435b08457866244502bcefe1589e6","tid":989864,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b9137de47f270795914a8c8db2a200c03cbc86","tid":989864,"uid":115949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"追住黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:37:48.000Z","msg":"追住來跪.....？<img src=\"/a